data.description: Seller offering $5,000 toward closing costs. Discover your dream home in this fully renovated 3-bedroom, 2-bath modern craftsman gem. Boasting a sleek metal roof, central heating and cooling for comfort, professionally installed carpet with tempurpedic padding in each bedroom and high-end laminate flooring that adds a touch of luxury. The 1532 sqft open-plan concept offers a natural light filled spacious living area that flows into the dining area and kitchen which boasts a walk-in pantry. The kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances and a utility room has been added for your convenience. Relax on the front covered porch adorned with gorgeous new wood beams or unwind on the water-sealed patio deck. This stunning property combines modern aesthetics with thoughtful upgrades, creating the perfect blend of style and functionality. Your dream home awaits! Call to set up a private tour! (grass enhanced in photos).
